text: Abdel Gawad () is an Egyptian surname. Notable people with this surname include: * Ahmed Abdel Gawad (died 2013), journalist, victim in the August 2013 Rabaa massacre * Heba Abdel Gawad (born 1982), Egyptian swimmer * Karim Abdel Gawad (born 1991), Egyptian squash player * Sara Abdel Gawad (born 1982), Egyptian swimmer * Zakaria Abdel Gawad, Egyptian novelist and journalist
title: Abdel Gawad
